-- Nava Bharat Ventures Drops Indonesia Coal, Power Projects, Mint Reports
-- B y   T h o m a s   A b r a h a m
-- 2010-11-09T01:02:22Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-09/nava-bharat-ventures-drops-indonesia-coal-power-projects-mint-reports.html
Nava Bharat Ventures Ltd. plans to
drop a coal mine and thermal power projects in Indonesia after
it failed to get a forest clearance and approval for tariffs,
the Mint reported, without saying where it got the information.  To contact the reporter on this story:
